Package org.jasig.portlet.courses.degreeprogress.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDegreeRequirement
    Gives information about a user's requirements for their degree.
    IGeneralDegreeRequirement
    An empty interface that extends IDegreeRequirement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CourseRequirement
    Holds the classes the user is registered for, and determines if they are completed.
    CreditsRequirement
    Holds the amount of the user's current credits towards an area of study and the amount of credits required for that area.
    DegreeProgramSummary
    Holds available programs, and the majors, minors and concentrations available.
    DegreeProgressReport
    Holds the Degree progress information, including the user's GPA and credit totals, and the corresponding requirements.
    DegreeRequirementSection
    Holds information regarding requirements for a degree choice.
    GpaRequirement
    Holds the user's current Grade Point Average (GPA) total and the required GPA total.
    ProgramComponent
    Holds information regarding program components (Majors, Minors and Concentrations).
